{"title":"Hexo + Gitpages完成个人博客搭建","date":"2018-05-25T10:46:00.000Z","author":"lycpang","excerpt":"","slug":"Hexo-Gitpages完成个人博客搭建","comments":true,"updated":"2018-05-25T11:00:08.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"Hexo-Gitpages完成个人博客搭建\"><a href=\"#Hexo-Gitpages完成个人博客搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo + Gitpages完成个人博客搭建\"></a>Hexo + Gitpages完成个人博客搭建</h1><h2 id=\"1-准备工作\"><a href=\"#1-准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.准备工作\"></a>1.准备工作</h2><ul>\n<li>github账号</li>\n<li>新建一个与github账号同名的库 <strong>账号id.github.io</strong></li>\n<li>node.js环境</li>\n<li>安装git</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-下载Hexo\"><a href=\"#2-下载Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.下载Hexo\"></a>2.下载Hexo</h2><p><code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-建站\"><a href=\"#3-建站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.建站\"></a>3.建站</h2><p><code>$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</code></p>\n<p><code>$ cd &lt;folder&gt;</code></p>\n<p><code>$ npm install</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-配置\"><a href=\"#4-配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.配置\"></a>4.配置</h2><h3 id=\"4-1配置-config-xml\"><a href=\"#4-1配置-config-xml\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.1配置_config.xml\"></a>4.1配置_config.xml</h3><p>参考：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configration.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configration.html</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"4-2配置github-ssh\"><a href=\"#4-2配置github-ssh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.2配置github ssh\"></a>4.2配置github ssh</h3><p>先安装hexo-deployer-git插件</p>\n<p><code>$ npm install hexo-deployer-git -save</code></p>\n<p>修改hexo的配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">\ttype: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">\trepo: &lt;repository git&gt; //SSH</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tbranch: [branch] //当前分支</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tmessage: [message] //可不填</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"4-3theme\"><a href=\"#4-3theme\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.3theme\"></a>4.3theme</h3><p>目录位置：主目录&gt;themes   <a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">theme</a></p>\n<p>执行代码<code>$ git clone &lt;theme github地址&gt;</code></p>\n<p>一般主题的about页面需要自己新建</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-主要命令\"><a href=\"#5-主要命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.主要命令\"></a>5.主要命令</h2><p>主目录初始化</p>\n<p><code>$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</code></p>\n<p>新建文章(layout可以省略)</p>\n<p><code>$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</code></p>\n<p>文章push到github上命令</p>\n<p><code>$ hexo clean</code><br><code>$ hexo g</code><br><code>$ hexo d</code>  </p>\n<h2 id=\"6-本地测试\"><a href=\"#6-本地测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.本地测试\"></a>6.本地测试</h2><p><code>$ hexo clean</code> 清除缓存<br><code>$ hexo g</code>  挂载<br><code>$ hexo s</code>  启动服务  </p>\n<p>执行完成之后访问  <a href=\"http://localhost:4000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">localhost:4000</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>注：匆匆记录一下过程，帮助意义不大。如需建站，谨慎使用。</p>\n","link":"http://yoursite.com/post/Hexo-Gitpages完成个人博客搭建"}